article_title: Carrollton man one of four arrested in prostitution sting
article_text:
Carrollton, GA (30117)

Today

Scattered clouds with the possibility of an isolated thunderstorm developing during the afternoon. High 86F. Winds SE at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 30%..

Tonight

Partly cloudy skies. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low 63F. Winds light and variable.

article_metadata.author: Colton Campbell/Times-Georgian

og.description: Four suspects, including a Carrollton man, have been arrested in a prostitution sting operation.
